description: STRAX AB specializes in mobile accessories and connected devices. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 231 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2000-04-25. The Company’s portfolio includes: Strax Group GmbH, a distributor of accessories for mobile devices such as mobile telephones and tablets; Swiss Picturebank AG which operates online storage and backup solutions by www.diino.com., a software application and online service that allows users to store, share, publish, and back up digital files, as well as WeSC AB, a lifestyle brand that has its roots in the skateboard culture and works with design, production and sales of clothes and accessories within the segment street fashion.
